  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Take a look at your opponents monitor to see what kind of image you need to match...</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349700/extras/55cf0311c150cd3a0730c18119427435.avif?t=1733749776\" width=616 height=346 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Start manipulating your monitor using your synthesizer! <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349700/extras/83570f9a88120505e2c195d3fe0b2a9b.avif?t=1733749776\" width=616 height=308 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >You have 60 seconds per puzzle, the closer the match, the higher the score!<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349700/extras/50f268ae565973ea62af2fcc32687380.avif?t=1733749776\" width=616 height=346 /></span> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each level adds more options for your synthesizer (and your opponents) for an added challenge!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Practice in the free mode, or see how long you can survive in the endless mode!<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349700/extras/be4b5ffdab92ea0bca312a17ea753d56.avif?t=1733749776\" width=616 height=346 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Enjoy the unique gameplay and aesthetic of 2Synth, complimented with music from artist \"LIFE PATTERNS\"<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349700/extras/57f462e4f93c930d936c29f6e4189b89.avif?t=1733749776\" width=616 height=122 /></span></h2>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Take a look at your opponents monitor to see what kind of image you need to match...</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349700/extras/55cf0311c150cd3a0730c18119427435.avif?t=1733749776\" width=616 height=346 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Start manipulating your monitor using your synthesizer! <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349700/extras/83570f9a88120505e2c195d3fe0b2a9b.avif?t=1733749776\" width=616 height=308 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >You have 60 seconds per puzzle, the closer the match, the higher the score!<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349700/extras/50f268ae565973ea62af2fcc32687380.avif?t=1733749776\" width=616 height=346 /></span> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each level adds more options for your synthesizer (and your opponents) for an added challenge!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Practice in the free mode, or see how long you can survive in the endless mode!<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349700/extras/be4b5ffdab92ea0bca312a17ea753d56.avif?t=1733749776\" width=616 height=346 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Enjoy the unique gameplay and aesthetic of 2Synth, complimented with music from artist \"LIFE PATTERNS\"<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349700/extras/57f462e4f93c930d936c29f6e4189b89.avif?t=1733749776\" width=616 height=122 /></span></h2>",
